Class FieldInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datalorax.populace.core.walk.field.FieldInfo

extends java.lang.Object

      • getGenericType

        public java.lang.reflect.Type getGenericType()
        Returns the generic type of the field, resolved using all available type information e.g. type variables are resolved where type information higher up the stack is available.
        • For primitive types this method returns the type of the field.
        • For non-primitive types with a null value this method returns the resolved generic type of the field
        • For non-primitive types with a non-null value this method returns the resolved generic type of the value
        Returns:
        the generic type of the field
        See Also:
        RawField.getGenericType()

      • getOwningInstance

        public java.lang.Object getOwningInstance()
        Returns the instance of this field's declaring class that this FieldInfo is wrapping.

        The type returned is guaranteed to be equal to or a sub type of the type returned by getDeclaringClass()

        Returns:
        the owning instance of the field
